itemContent:
First, awesome with the hits. The pay's perfect (assuming, you know, I don't get rejected offhand, then it's not so nice).  Music HITs are great.  It's nice there's such a huge timer. The interface is pretty decent, as well.

But.

There's nothing showing you where you're at in the song. That'd be really helpful. There's also no instructions for what sort of feedback is desired/appreciated.

Also, if the artists want more feedback, it'd be helpful to be able to rate it within some categories. 

And, finally, it'd be nice if your interface remembered the stats of the turkers doing your hits (\PickFu\" does this
DateCreated: etc).  My age only changes once a year
